before installation of master and slave config 
create a instance in aws and launch it
next run it and click on connect and open git bash in local machine where our .pem file is located
next copy the example link from connect option in chrome and paste it on git bash prompt
and type yes and enter
now the instance connected to local machine
now give command sudo -i or sudo su -
this will direct the root user 
now create one directory by using mkdir <file name>
now enter into that directory via cd <file name>
now install java jdk file and check it running status via java -version or javac
if it is running now configure the root path and details of slave machine in master machine at node creation.
